{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>This is not just another burger joint </strong>\ud83c\udf54</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After pushing open this door for the 798th time, you might realize: the menu only ever has cheeseburgers, the server's smile seems nailed to their face, and the world outside... appears to change subtly with each visit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to &quot;Can I Buy You A Cheeseburger?&quot; \u2014 a twisted adventure on the edge of consciousness \ud83c\udf00</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore a Crumbling Reality</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a psychological journey between reality and illusion</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve puzzles in peculiar ways to rediscover the true face of this world</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Live through one person's terrible day, feel the absurdity and emptiness of life</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your choices will shape the story until you face final redemption... or destruction</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unique Gaming Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf54 <strong>Narrative</strong>: A postmodern, stream-of-consciousness storytelling experience (Memories might be false, but the cheeseburger is real)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf54 <strong>Puzzles</strong>: Search for truth in a warped world, rethink your understanding of &quot;puzzles&quot; (Don't worry about finding the truth - it's also looking for you)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf54 <strong>Art</strong>: Figurative expressionist style presenting a distorted yet dynamic visual world (It's okay if you don't understand it - we didn't either while drawing it)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>This is for you if you</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel life is meaningless</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy stories but seek no logic</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Love thinking but seek no answers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Love puzzles but seek no solutions</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Value art but seek no understanding</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy David Lynch-style surreal experiences</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are willing to explore the boundaries of humanity and reality</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find yourself having a terrible day and needing a... cheeseburger \ud83c\udf54</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Today's Menu \ud83d\udccb</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Delicious cheeseburger \ud83c\udf54</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An experiment in game narrative \ud83d\udd2c</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The creator's chaotic mental state \ud83e\udd2a</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A transcendent gaming experience \ud83c\udfae</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some psychological horror elements \ud83d\udc7b</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;The world is burning, but at least we still have cheeseburgers.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2014 Final words from a customer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finally, remember:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Life is chaotic, absurd, and meaningless. Life is a cheeseburger.</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735894181","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229220/page.bg.jpg?t=1735894181","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229220/84a5355e10ab93c56965fa760b7389b824d242a3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735894181","ca